column2: Army is the PICA for this item; therefore, the Air Force requirements are ordered against contracts awarded by the Army. Due to a contractor protest, the Army awarded to 2 contractors ILO a single contractor. The Air Force requirements will be awarded to either FN Manufacturing,Columbia, SC or to Colt, Hartford, CT for FY16-FY18.
